snippet.title: Best VGM 496 - Lunar : Dragon Song - Wind of Future
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 975 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q1TnrjE909c

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Lunar: Dragon Song
Wind of Future (Look For an Exciting New World!)
